parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
or the airbag deploys unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall has led to a shortage of replacement parts, causing delays and inconvenience to vehicle owners.
symptoms: Vehicle owners receive recall notifications but are unable to have the repairs done due to parts unavailability
leading to safety concerns and frustration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the SRS light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which may not deploy in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The SRS light is illuminated on the instrument panel
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag does not deploy in a crash
or the airbag deploys incorrectly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power window master switch can cause the windows to malfunction, leading to inconvenience, and in some cases, a fire hazard.
symptoms: The power window switch emits smoke
the window becomes stuck
or the switch fails to operate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various components to malfunction, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The instrument panel flickers
the vehicle stalls
the airbag warning indicator illuminates
and the interior lights fail to operate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to malfunction, leading to inconvenience and safety risks.
symptoms: The door locks fail to operate
the key becomes stuck
and the door fails to open manually.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The key fails to turn in the ignition
the ignition switch overheats
and the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or fail to deploy in the event of a crash, leading to safety risks.
symptoms: The airbag warning indicator illuminates
and the airbag fails to deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioner compressor can cause the air conditioning system to malfunction, leading to discomfort and potential health risks, especially in hot weather conditions.
symptoms: The air conditioner blows hot air
makes loud grinding or clunking noises
or fails to turn on. In some cases
the compressor may seize or implode
causing damage to other components of the air conditioning system.
